            </nav>  
            <div id="grid-pagina">
                <section id="prezentare">
                    <h2>Bine ati venit!</h2>
                    <%/*%><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Buton</button><%*/%>
                    <p>Va multumim ca ati ales site-ul BBallStore pentru a va achizitiona articolele de baschet!</p>
                    <q>I've failed over and over and over again in my life. And that is why I succeed.</q> - Michael Jordan<br/>
