                                <tr><td colspan="4">Programul poate oricand sa sufere modificari!</td></tr>
                            </tfoot>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section id="diverse">
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>BBallStore</b> este un magazin, fizic sau online, de articole sportive de baschet, fondat in anul 2024.</li>
                        <li>Magazinul contine incaltaminte, pantaloni, tricouri, <i>jersey-uri</i> si accesorii precum: minge, genunchiere, cotiere, sosete, toate fiind de specialitate. Cateva dintre firmele prezente in depozitul nostru sunt: Nike, Adidas, Under Armour, Anta, Reebok, Puma si nu numai.</li>
                        <li>Acest magazin are o locatie in Bucuresti si ofera atat optiunea de a prelua articolele fizic, cat si <strong>transport la domiciliu</strong> oriunde in tara.</li>
                        <li><em>Totul despre excelenta!</em></li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="container-iframe">
                        <div class="taburi-iframe">
                            <a class="tab1" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_Q8obt4xuEw?si=AuDEZQMO1gJPluSN" target="ifr-v1">Video 1</a>
                            <a class="tab2" href="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mtIdBf_e1NM?si=PKCMAleGLSnw2lQ6" target="ifr-v1">Video 2</a>
                        </div>
                        <iframe class="video-iframe" name="ifr-v1" width="400" height="300" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mtIdBf_e1NM?si=PKCMAleGLSnw2lQ6" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
